    //   4. If elements[0] is alone in one group, and elements[1] is in the other group with other elements,
    //      min_f = elements[0].value + elements[1].value + h.
    //   5. If elements[0] and elements[1] are in the same group, and this group has other elements,
    //      min_f = elements[0].value + elements[1].value.

