    //    Consider the partition where `elements[0]` is in group 1, and all other elements are in group 2.
    //    Group 1: {elements[0]}
    //    Group 2: {elements[1], elements[2], ..., elements[n-1]}
    //    (This requires n >= 2. If n=2, G1={elements[0]}, G2={elements[1]}. No same-group pairs. min_f = elements[0]+elements[1]+h, max_f = elements[0]+elements[1]+h. Goodness = 0.)
    //    (If n=3, G1={elements[0]}, G2={elements[1], elements[2]}.
