        // i=2: a[2]='0', b[2]='1'. Pending 1->0. Use it. current_diff_10 becomes 0.
        //      This resolves (1->0) at index 1 and (0->1) at index 2.
        //      This is a swap. Cost of this swap is |1-2|=1. Add to total cost.
        //      cost = 1.
        //      (current_diff_01=0, current_diff_10=0)
        // i=3: a[3]='1', b[3]='1'. Match. cost=1.
        //      (current_diff_01=0, current_diff_10=0)
        // Total cost = 1. This matches example.

